{"TopicId":176732,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Formation Flight","CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-15T04:56:37Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-15T04:56:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks to a \u00A0little trick I learned from\u00A0this \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-9lPFZ3i-pk\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Evideo\u003C/a\u003E,\u00A0\u00A0 I got my trio of aircraft flying together.\u00A0(L to R \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Klapaucius/The-Professor\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThe Professor\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Klapaucius/Lerxst\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ELerxst \u003C/a\u003E\u0026amp; \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Klapaucius/Geddy\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGeddy\u003C/a\u003E).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022BUd5gkc.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/BUd5gkc.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225MN6Wpu.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5MN6Wpu.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ss4DJeu.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ss4DJeu.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-18T17:19:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will be frank, these are very cool designs - almost like a combination between a cheesy space opera and something Gru will fly, but much smoother and sleeker. I think my favorite will be the Geddy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-18T19:41:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223417751\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176732\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221531934349\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will be frank, these are very cool designs - almost like a combination between a cheesy space opera and something Gru will fly, but much smoother and sleeker. I think my favorite will be the Geddy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the kind comment!\u00A0 I really enjoy coming up with odd ideas and then seeing if I can make functional aircraft out of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-07-18T19:42:12Z\u0022 title=\u002207/18/2018 07:42  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 18, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-19T08:12:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223417751\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022176732\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221531934349\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think my favorite will be the Geddy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve made a few planes with that configuration. I like the big wings because they are large lifting fuel tanks, so I tend to use them a lot which saves me having to add additional tanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe first one, \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Klapaucius/Phlebas-16-passenger-short-haul-flying-contraption\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EPhlebas\u003C/a\u003E, is horrendously inefficient, but a lot fun.\u00A0 The second, \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalx.com/Klapaucius/Groucho-32-passenger-seaplane\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGroucho\u003C/a\u003E, takes the same idea and incorporates it into a seaplane.\u00A0 It is not amazingly efficient either, but it flies really well and has a low stall speed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022f0kY1bx.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/f0kY1bx.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022WnAc9l9.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/WnAc9l9.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XLjedi","CreatedById":175658,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-19T15:23:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool!\u00A0 I once did something similar for\u00A0a Kerbal\u00A0airshow. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-22T04:33:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose look great! By the way, editor extensions redux lets you use the offset tool without limits, and burn together (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/PapaJoesSoup/BurnTogether/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Elink\u003C/a\u003E because it\u0027s hard to track down a up to date version) or BD armory\u0027s wing commander lets you make formation flights more easily.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}